{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"A\n    \n      SVG Path + stroke-dashoffset (Recommended)\n      How: A single full-page SVG overlay with a cubic Bezier curve. Uses motion/react's useScroll + useTransform to map scroll progress to stroke-dashoffset, creating a draw-on reveal.\n      \n        \n          Pros\n          \n            Smooth, precise scroll-linked animation (no jank)\n            Already proven in your Approach section's river-path\n            Uses existing motion/react library — no new deps\n            SVG gradient ribbon via linearGradient + wider stroke\n            Fully responsive — path recalculated on resize\n          \n        \n        \n          Cons\n          \n            Path coordinates need calculation relative to section positions\n            Full-page SVG overlay needs careful z-indexing","choice":"a","id":null,"timestamp":1773216236794}
